                    <p class="point" data-map-point="7"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="8"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="9"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="10"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="11"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="12"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="13"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="14"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="15"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="16"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="17"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="18"></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="floor-map floor-3F js-switch-tab" data-tab-id="3">
                <picture>
                    <img src="/assets/images/top/map-3f.png" srcset="/assets/images/top/map-3f@2x.png 2x" alt="空庭ヒーローズ">
                </picture>
                <div class="floor-map_points">
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="19"></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="floor-map floor-4F5F js-switch-tab" data-tab-id="4">
                <picture>
                    <img src="/assets/images/top/map-4f5f.png" srcset="/assets/images/top/map-4f5f@2x.png 2x" alt="空庭ヒーローズ">
                </picture>
                <div class="floor-map_points">
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="20"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="21"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="22"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="23"></p>
                    <p class="point" data-map-point="24"></p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="floor-map_nav" data-floor-nav="2,4">
                <p class="floor-map-btn -prev"></p>
                <p class="floor-map-btn -next"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="floor-map_modal">
                <div class="floor-map_modal-block">
                    <a href="" class="close"></a>
                    <%- include('./_include/index_floor') %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="news">
        <div class="news-list">
            <div class="news-item">
                <a href="./news/heroes.html">
                    <picture>
                        <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/assets/images/top/news-heroes-sp.jpg">
                        <img src="/assets/images/top/news-heroes.jpg" alt="空庭ヒーローズ">
                    </picture>
                    <p>空庭ヒーローズ</p>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="news-item">
                <a href="./news/onsen.html">
                    <picture>
                        <source media="(max-width: 768px)" srcset="/assets/images/top/news-onsen-sp.jpg">
                        <img src="/assets/images/top/news-onsen.jpg" alt="空庭温泉で美味しく、愉しく、美しく">
                    </picture>
                    <p>空庭温泉で<br><span>美味しく、愉しく、</span><br class="sp">美しく</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="guide">
        <div class="sec-title">営業案内</div>
        <div class="guide-list">
            <div class="guide-item -time">
                <p class="guide-item_icon"><img src="/assets/images/cmn/icn-guide-time.svg" alt="Time"></p>
                <dl class="guide-item_info">
                    <dt>11:00～翌9:00</dt>
                    <dd>16歳未満のみのご利用は夜19時まで、<br class="sp">18歳未満のみのご利用は夜22時までです。</dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="guide-item -station">
                <p class="guide-item_icon"><img src="/assets/images/cmn/icn-guide-station.svg" alt="Station"></p>
                <dl class="guide-item_info">
                    <dt>弁天町駅:<br>JR大阪環状線・大阪メトロ中央線</dt>
                    <dd>連絡通路直結<br>
                        大阪駅（梅田）から約10分 /<br>
                        関西国際空港から約60分
                    </dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="guide-item -location">
                <p class="guide-item_icon"><img src="/assets/images/cmn/icn-guide-location.svg" alt="Location"></p>
                <dl class="guide-item_info">
                    <dt>大阪府大阪市<br>港区弁天1丁目2-3</dt>
                    <dd><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/bK8VPYoAMh62" target="_blank">Google mapで見る</a></dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="guide-item -parking">
                <p class="guide-item_icon"><img src="/assets/images/cmn/icn-guide-parking.svg" alt="Parking"></p>
                <dl class="guide-item_info">
                    <dt>近隣の駐車場</dt>
                    <dd><a href="http://baytower.jp/parking/" target="_blank">詳しくはこちら</a></dd>
                </dl>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('./_include/footer',{lower:0}) %>

    <%- include('./_include/navFix',{isTop:1}) %>

